name: SearchSuggestTest - first item
description: The term suggester provides a very convenient API to access word alternatives on token basis within a certain string distance. The API allows accessing each token in the stream individually while suggest-selection is left to the API consumer. Yet, often pre-selected suggestions are required in order to present to the end-user.
